The torrent above contained around 450 issues of the X-men from 1963 onward but was in PDF format. I took all the PDF&amp;#039;s, converted them to JPG&amp;#039;s and packed them into CBZ&amp;#039;s so they could be read by the various comic viewers out there (CDDisplay, ComicRack, etc.) I also broke it up by the decades so it would be easier to download than the original 5 gig download.

All credit for this goes to the original uploader and/or scanner. I just did the conversion from PDF to JPG and packed them. Of course I did this over 450 times. :)

*Note
I have done all the decades, I just started with this one as it was requested.
